    "aliasEn": "Crimson",
    "biomeType": "crimson",
    "code": "crimson",
    "description": "The Crimson is an evil biome with a fleshy infection, red gore theme, in contrast to the dark purple wasteland theme of its counterpart, the Corruption . Every world will contain one of the two generated randomly except for special seeds (each with a 50% chance of occurring) or chosen by the player upon world creation. Both contain similar hazards and feature their own unique enemies , items , and blocks . The tools , weapons , and armor obtained via Crimson material generally have minor advantages over those obtained via Corruption materials; however, Corruption tools are slightly faster. Crimson-themed enemies also tend to have slightly higher stats, such as health, defense, and damage.",
