    "code": "jungle",
    "description": "The Jungle is a surface biome composed primarily of Mud Blocks with Jungle grass and Jungle vines , with a dark green background. Mahogany trees are abundant there, as they grow automatically on Jungle grass, though traditional Acorns can also be planted. Moreover, many pools of water can be found in the Jungle, often with several Bamboo stalks. The Underground Jungle is found just below the Jungle, beginning at cavern depths.",
